metadata.name: Raising the Work
metadata.description:
It is hard work to keep your constructions stabilized without losing their charm. It takes balance and a connection to the environment. Know the winds, the rains, and to be sure that nothing can bring your construction down.

Ariel Gricio | 2022  
Ubatuba | Brazil  
Digital Photography
